ily again.\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being able not to miss little memories, things that I took for granted that I do not take for granted anymore,\\\" Griner said.\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1618, \"end\": 1624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Griner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The gold (medal game) is just the icing on the cake, being in the Olympics\\u2026 as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A train trip to Lille, where the group stage of the Olympic tournament was played, briefly reminded Griner of her time in Russia.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1820, \"end\": 1826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Griner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\"}, {\"begin\": 1842, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9985576862280466, \"rank\": 0.0007657621733614252, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had not traveled on a railway since a Russian train took her to a prison colony in 2022.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1892, \"end\": 1899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9975401425079733, \"rank\": 0.0019887888997678076, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia